Anyone who knows me knows my passion for food and eating out 🍽️ 
@coachdagod and I decided we’d share some of our favorite places with you throughout NY and NJ. 
📌 Tag a restaurant you’d like to see us feature

#foodies #foodporn #foodblogger #foodphotography #food #foodstagram #diningout #photography #passion #eat #eatingout #eatlocal #supportsmallbusiness

This is how we Taco Tuesday 🌮 if you haven’t tried @crafttaqueria yet- this is your sign 

📍170 South Main Street, New City, NY 10956 
🎥 @coachdagod 

Craft Taqueria is a hidden gem right in New City, NY 💎Chef Jeff clearly is passionate about his restaurant-from the details in the decor to the ingredients used in his menu.  The Grilled Spanish Octopus 🐙which was made with house made chorizo, epazote crema and crispy sweet potatoes is a must have.  Our all time favorite is the Birria, which is made of short ribs and oxtails. 
🍷and don’t forget to try the house made Sangria which is the perfect blend of fruit, wine and happiness 🥰 
And make sure you top it off with your best flan you’ll ever have 🍮

#tacos #tacotuesday #tacosofinstagram #foodie #foodporn #foodblogger #views #rockland #influencer #restaurants #dining #sangria #birria #guacamole #dessert #contentcreator #socialmedia #socialmediamanager #photooftheday

What happens when you take the delicacy of mochi and the savory flavors of a donut and combine them together? 
You get a Mochinut 🍩 @mochinut_newcity 

📍 170 S. Main Street, New City, NY 10956
🎥 @coachdagod 

It was a fun experience getting behind the scenes with the owner, Kristine, who showed us how everything was made. It was impressive to see how she dips these donuts herself daily with so many creative flavors.  We truly enjoyed every flavor that Mochinut New City offered, but my favorite was the Vietnamese Coffee and the Raspberry Funnel Cake. 
You have to try their corn dogs🌭 I had the potato half and half-which was half hot dog and half mozzarella cheese and covered in potatoes on the outside. So delish ‼️ And they also have bubble tea 🧋and even have dairy free options. 

#donut #mochi #mochinut #dessert #corndog #bubbletea #bubbletealover #dairyfree #eatdessertfirst #foodie #foodporn #foodblogger #photooftheday #entrepreneur

Life is too short to miss out on double cheeseburgers🍔

@mashedburgers 
📍 652 Anderson Avenue, Cliffside Park, NJ 
🎥 @coachdagod 

If you’re in the mood for a burger, you should check out the recently opened Mashed Burger located right in the heart of Cliffside Park, NJ.  This burger hits all the right spots.  The double cheeseburger was cooked to perfection and topped with melted cheese, grilled onions, pickles and a special sauce.  And don’t forget, everything gets better with a milkshake.  Indulge in a fruity pebbles milkshake, you deserve it🥤

#burger #burgerporn #burgerlife #burgers #burgertime #burgerlovers #bergencounty #foodie #foodporn #foodblogger #food #instagram #milkshake #fruitypebbles

Always make time for things you cherish…like tacos 🌮 😃

🌮 @el_tacobar 
📍244 Closter Dock Rd, Closter, NJ
🎥 @coachdagod 

El Taco Bar is about total authenticity.  From the handmade tortillas to the special house salsas, every bite was scrumptious. We especially loved the loaded fries with  rotisserie marinated pork🤤 and the shrimp tacos with pineapple pico de gallo topped with creamy chipotle sauce. 

#taco #tacos #tacotuesday #birria #loadedfries #foodie #foodporn #foodblogger #foodstagram #insta #instafood 
#shrimp #shrimptacos #tacotuesday🌮 #delicious

Follow your heart, but take a cup of coffee with you ☕️❤️

☕️ @doyoujavalove 
📍 50 Lafayette Ave, Suffern, NY 
🎥 @coachdagod 

Java Love Coffee Roasting company offers much more than just coffee…. And they have four locations and are woman-owned. We visited the Suffern, NY location ☕️ 
We started off with an Acai Peanut Butter Smoothie Bowl. It was simply delicious 😊 They offer a great variety of breakfast options from traditional with eggs potatoes and toast to French toast or pancakes. For lunch, I highly recommend the grilled chicken melt with a side of potatoes. It was delicious. 😋We loved the refreshing cold beverages such as the Iced Tea Palmer with a splash of strawberry🍓 if you’re into hot beverages, you should try the classic hot latte ☕️

Life is all about discovering new tastes🥢 🍸

🍽️ @kantinany 
📍 4 Depot Square, Sparkill
🎥 @coachdagod 

If you’re looking for the perfect place for date night or girls night out- this is it‼️ I don’t know about you… but I personally really care about the setting and ambience of the environment. How it feels to be there… 🪷Kantina nailed it. They offer indoor and outdoor dining along with a full bar and an intimate cocktail lounge.  Chef and owner, Chris Holland, a 3x Food Network Chopped Champion, offers a unique Asian twist on small plates, tacos and more.  I especially loved the Cauliflower arepas and Red beet hand rolls.  The Korean Hot Chicken Takos were my favorite. They are cornflake crusted topped with homemade kimchi and chili oil. Kantina’s drink menu offers a taste of Heaven 🍹If you’re not driving lol, I recommend the Paradise Punch. It’s sweet and spicy which matches my personality perfect 🙃 I recommend making reservations but walk ins are welcome too 

#foodie #foodporn #outdoordining #asian #tacos #drinkmenu #cocktails #cocktailporn #yummy #vegan #supportlocal #fyp #restaurants

You know it’s happiness when it’s served slow-smoked and sauced 🍽️

📍 900 Route 17 North, Ramsey, NJ
🎥 @coachdagod 

If you’re hungry… this is the place to be 🍴Brothers Smokehouse BBQ & Soul is hands down one of the best BBQ restaurants in Bergen County.  And I have great news - there’s a new location coming to Palisades Mall this year ‼️I highly recommend starting with their mouthwatering cornbread. And do not miss out on their sticky ribs. They are smoked and caramelized in their house bbq sauce.  If you’re into wings, you have to try their award winning garlic thyme 🍗 My favorite at Brothers is the 3 meat combo where you get to choose three of your favorite smoked meats with two sides.  Whatever you do, don’t skip dessert.  Their homemade bread pudding is delish 😋

Get your stretchy pants ready because you won’t be able to eat just one slice @grumpysnj 

📍 522 Saddle River Road, Saddle Brook 
🎥 @coachdagod 

There’s no pizza like sourdough pizza! 🍕With a crispy, chewy crust that is perfectly charred on top and bottom and loaded with all the good stuff.  With San Marzano-style tomatoes, the meat lovers 🥩🥓to meat haters 🫑🍅 (all veggies) square or round, we loved it all.  The owner, Marcello has truly mastered making the best crust.  I loved that there is a choice of either round, square or personal and each crust tastes different depending on the shape. And it doesn’t stop there- all of their subs are also made on homemade sourdough bread cooked to perfection. Whatever you do- don’t skip dessert- the fried Oreos with white chocolate drizzle were the best I’ve ever had.
